<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.1">
<l>ēṟāḷu miṟaiyōṉun ticaimukaṉun tirumakaḷuṅ</l>
<l>kūṟāḷun taṉiyuṭampaṉ kulaṅkulamā vacurarkaḷai</l>
<l>nīṟākum paṭiyāka nirumittup paṭaitoṭṭa</l>
<l>māṟāḷaṉ kavarāta maṇimāmai kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one whose single body controls as parts the lord who rules the bull</l>
<l>and the one with faces in the directions and the woman Śrī, the contrary man</l>
<l>linked with a weapon, determined that there be a way that the Asuras become ashes</l>
<l>clan by clan, we have no want for [our] sapphire darkness not seized by him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
